row.entry:
Unsigned
integer that specifies a number of hours. Used as a starting field, hours can have up to 18 digits if no end-field exists;
16 digits if minutes is the end-field;
and 14-f digits if seconds is the end-field, where f is the fraction less than or equal to 6. These maximums are specified by HOUR(18),
HOUR(16) TO MINUTE, and HOUR(14-f) TO SECOND(f). Used as an ending field, the value of hours must be in the range 0 to 23.

